Sarkozy to Meet Merkel in Coming Days on Fiscal Integration Push

-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 
2011-09-30T16:15:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/sarkozy-to-meet-merkel-in-coming-days-on-fiscal-integration-push.html
French President  Nicolas Sarkozy 
said he’ll meet German Chancellor  Angela Merkel  in Berlin in
coming days to address accelerating fiscal integration in
 Europe . Speaking to reporters in Paris after meeting Greek
Premier  George Papandreou , Sarkozy said Europe had an “economic
and moral duty” to continue supporting  Greece ’s economy.
Greece’s failure would mean the “failure of Europe,” Sarkozy
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helene Fouquet in Paris at 
 hfouquet1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
